VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)secret_key_base\s*[:=]\s*["'](?:changeme|secret|test|default)["']
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:secret_key_base\s*[:=]\s*["'](changeme|secret|test|default|password|123)["']|SECRET_KEY_BASE.*=.*["']\w{4,20}["'] && MISSING:Rails\.application\.credentials|ENV\[|ENV\.fetch
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects likely weak or default session secret values.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Weak Session Secret Configuration.
